| Kethloryn | Spider prophecy, venom | Ssyraeth (Venom-Seer) | Spider-type monsters, venom creatures |
| Bressarai | Aesthetic cruelty, poison | Vaelissar (Gilded Rot) | Poison creatures, torture constructs |
| Buarath | Flesh-warping, grafts | Buaress (Many-Mask) | Flesh golems, mutated aberrations, grafted horrors |
